modified: 20260424155200000
type: text/markdown

add a code block in called `#+BEGIN_HTML` and write your own html code in.

example: (remove commas)

``` org
#+BEGIN_EXPORT html
,<img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41zeL13jFOL._SY445_SX342_FMwebp_.jpg" alt="Image" />
#+END_EXPORT
```
